      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "PAS DE CHEVAL (2) has the hoof on the till after finishing runner-up in her last two outings at this venue, last week coming from this barrier and using the sprint lane to be beaten 1.6 metres. Eases back a little in grade so gets her chance to break through. SHAZADELE (8) made it if four placings in a row at this circuit when she settled back from this barrier but worked home in good style to finish 1.1 metres from the winner in second. If things go her way she could break through. HOLY CAMP DILLON (1) was solid from much wider here last week. Has won twice at this longer distance here and draws to be competitive. RONZEL SONNY (7) cops a wider draw but is tough to leave out after winning his last two.",
